    public static interface DeferredImportSelector.Group
    Interface used to group results from different import selectors.

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static class  DeferredImportSelector.Group.Entry
      An entry that holds the AnnotationMetadata of the importing Configuration class and the class name to import.
